## Roadmap by Version

### v1.1 (April-May 2024) - User Experience
**Goal:** Make VIBE sticky—users want to come back and save their work.

#### Features

- [ ] **User Accounts & Authentication**
  - GitHub/Google login (easier than email)
  - Profile and project management
  - Writing history and saved drafts

- [ ] **Export Functionality**
  - Download as `.txt`, `.docx`, `.pdf`
  - One-click export to Google Docs
  - Email drafts to yourself

- [ ] **Community Prompt Library**
  - Browse prompts shared by other writers
  - Rate and review prompts
  - Search by genre and style

- [ ] **Enhanced UI/UX**
  - Dark mode support
  - Keyboard shortcuts
  - Customizable editor preferences

#### Priority Issues
- [ ] #15: Add user authentication
- [ ] #24: Implement export to Word
- [ ] #31: Build prompt library UI
- [ ] #42: Add dark mode

---

### v2.0 (June-August 2024) - Collaboration & Community
**Goal:** Transform VIBE into a collaborative platform where writers support each other.

#### Features

- [ ] **Real-Time Collaborative Editing**
  - Multiple writers working on same project
  - Live cursor positions and comments
  - Conflict resolution (last-write-wins)
  - Built with WebSockets

- [ ] **Writing Analytics Dashboard**
  - Word count tracking
  - Writing streak counter
  - Progress toward goals
  - Time spent writing

- [ ] **Peer Review System**
  - Request feedback from community writers
  - Anonymous reviewer matching
  - Structured review templates
  - Rating and appreciation system

- [ ] **AI Fine-Tuning**
  - Train models on user preferences
  - Remember writing style
  - Personalized suggestions
  - Better feedback over time

- [ ] **Community Publishing**
  - Share finished stories publicly (optional)
  - Showcase and trending stories
  - Genre-based discovery
  - Reader comments and feedback

#### Technical Goals
- [ ] Implement WebSocket server for real-time sync
- [ ] Add database support (PostgreSQL)
- [ ] Build analytics service
- [ ] Set up AI fine-tuning pipeline

---

### v3.0 (Fall 2024+) - Advanced Features
**Goal:** Become the go-to platform for writers of all levels.

#### Potential Features

- **Mobile Apps** - Native iOS/Android apps for writing on-the-go
- **AI Voice** - Read feedback and suggestions aloud
- **Research Assistant** - Built-in research tool for historical/factual accuracy
- **Translation Tools** - Write in one language, publish in many
- **Academic Integration** - Direct submission to university writing centers
- **Publishing Integration** - Connect to indie publishing platforms
- **Community Challenges** - Monthly writing prompts and competitions
- **Workshops & Courses** - Educational content from published authors

